"{\"uid\": \"horseandhound.co.uk-features-olympic-cross-country-day-paris-865448\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Tomorrow is one of the biggest days in horse sport, one that only comes round every four (well, three on this occasion) years - it's Olympic cross-country day for the eventers.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 176, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tomorrow\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 8}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest days\", \"from\": 19, \"to\": 35}, {\"ngram\": \"horse sport\", \"from\": 39, \"to\": 50}, {\"ngram\": \"this occasion\", \"from\": 105, \"to\": 118}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic cross-country day\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 158}, {\"ngram\": \"the eventers\", \"from\": 163, \"to\": 175}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, if you are tuning into the action from theParis Gamesat home, what should you look out for?\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 273, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 215}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Gamesat home\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read on, we have got you covered\\u2026 1.\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 313, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The beauty of thecross-country course.\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 352, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The beauty\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 324}, {\"ngram\": \"thecross-country course\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pierre Le Goupil's track has been decorated to fit in with the French theme and particularlythe history of Versailles- you can admire fences such as the Enlightenment Bookcase and the Etoile Royal Waters.\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 363, \"end\": 369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goupil_&_Cie\", \"score\": 0.9935874826063947, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Goupil\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goupil_&_Cie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goupil_&_Cie\"}, {\"begin\": 416, \"end\": 4